'''檜木醇'''，又称'''日柏酚'''（{{lang-en|Hinokitiol}}，β-侧柏素，β-thujaplicin）是在[[柏科|柏科]]（Cupressaceae）的树木中发现的一种天然[[萜烯|单萜]]<ref>[https://www.sigmaaldrich.com/US/en/product/aldrich/469521 "β-Thujaplicin at Sigma-Aldrich"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sigmaaldrich.com/catalog/ProductDetail.do?N4=469521%7CALDRICH&N5=SEARCH_CONCAT_PNO%7CBRAND_KEY&F=SPEC |date=20110716071442 }}, ''sigmaaldrich.com''.</ref>。 它是[[托酚酮|托酚酮]]衍生物，是三种{{le|侧柏素|Thujaplicin}}中的一种<ref>Chedgy RJ, Lim YW, Breuil C (May 2009). "Effects of leaching on fungal growth and decay of western redcedar". Canadian Journal of Microbiology. 55 (5): 578–86. [https://doi.org/10.1139%2FW08-161 doi:10.1139/W08-161]. PMID [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19483786 19483786] {{Wayback|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19483786 |date=20210810221447 }}.</ref>。 Hinokitiol因其广谱抗病毒<ref>Krenn BM, Gaudernak E, Holzer B, Lanke K, Van Kuppeveld FJ, Seipelt J (January 2009). "[https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18922875/ Antiviral activity of the zinc ionophores pyrithione and hinokitiol against picornavirus infections] {{Wayback|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18922875/ |date=20211021223616 }}". Journal of Virology. 83 (1): 58–64. [https://doi.org/10.1128%2FJVI.01543-08 doi:10.1128/JVI.01543-08]. PMC [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2612303 2612303] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2612303 |date=20210907103808 }}. PMID [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18922875 18922875] {{Wayback|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18922875 |date=20211021223616 }}</ref>，抗菌<ref>Inamori Y, Shinohara S, Tsujibo H, Okabe T, Morita Y, Sakagami Y, et al. (September 1999). "[https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10513629/ Antimicrobial activity and metalloprotease inhibition of hinokitiol-related compounds, the constituents of Thujopsisdolabrata S. and Z. hondai MAK] {{Wayback|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10513629/ |date=20200617044420 }}". Biological & Pharmaceutical Bulletin. 22 (9): 990–3. [https://doi.org/10.1248%2Fbpb.22.990 doi:10.1248/bpb.22.990]. PMID [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10513629 10513629] {{Wayback|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10513629 |date=20201005074820 }}.</ref>和抗炎<ref>Ye J, Xu YF, Lou LX, Jin K, Miao Q, Ye X, Xi Y (July 2015). "[https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25952949/ Anti-inflammatory effects of hinokitiol on human corneal epithelial cells: an in vitro study] {{Wayback|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25952949/ |date=20201005083408 }}". Eye. 29 (7): 964–71. [https://doi.org/10.1038%2Feye.2015.62 doi:10.1038/eye.2015.62]. PMC [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4506343 4506343] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4506343 |date=20210302100729 }}. PMID [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25952949 25952949] {{Wayback|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25952949 |date=20201005083408 }}.</ref>作用而被广泛用于口腔护理和治疗产品。Hinokitiol是锌和铁的离子载体，此外，它还被批准用作食品添加剂<ref>"[https://dx.doi.org/10.7143/jhep.43.299 Stress Check System]". Health evaluation and promotion. 43 (2): 299–303. 2016. [https://doi.org/10.7143%2Fjhep.43.299 doi:10.7143/jhep.43.299]. ISSN [https://www.worldcat.org/issn/1347-0086 1347-0086] {{Wayback|url=https://www.worldcat.org/issn/1347-0086 |date=20200728133452 }}</ref>。

Hinokitiol的名称起源于1936年最初在[[台湾扁柏|台湾扁柏]]中分离<ref>Murata I, Itô S, Asao T (December 2012). "Tetsuo Nozoe: chemistry and life". Chemical Record. 12 (6): 599–607. [https://doi.org/10.1002%2Ftcr.201200024 doi:10.1002/tcr.201200024]. PMID [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23242794 23242794].</ref>。实际上，在日本扁柏中它几乎不存在，而其含量高（约占心材质量的0.04％）存在于Junipruscedrus和Hiba柏木中。 （Thujopsisdolabrata）和西部红柏（Thujaplicata）。可以很容易地通过溶剂和超声从雪松中提取。<ref>Chedgy RJ, Daniels CR, Kadla J, Breuil C (2007). "Screening fungi tolerant to Western red cedar (Thujaplicata Donn) extractives. Part 1. Mild extraction by ultrasonication and quantification of extractives by reverse-phase HPLC". Holzforschung. 61 (2): 190–194. [https://doi.org/10.1515%2FHF.2007.033 doi:10.1515/HF.2007.033]</ref>

Hinokitiol在结构上与tropolone有关，后者缺少异丙基取代基。Tropolones是众所周知的[[螯合剂|螯合剂]]。

==抗菌活性==
Hinokitiol具有广泛的生物学活性，许多生物学活性已在文献中进行了探索和表征。首先，也是最广为人知的是，不管抗生素是否耐药，其对许多细菌和真菌的有效抗菌活性。<ref>Shih YH, Chang KW, Hsia SM, Yu CC, Fuh LJ, Chi TY, Shieh TM (June 2013). "In vitro antimicrobial and anticancer potential of hinokitiol against oral pathogens and oral cancer cell lines". Microbiological Research. 168 (5): 254–62. [https://doi.org/10.1016%2Fj.micres.2012.12.007 doi:10.1016/j.micres.2012.12.007]. PMID [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23312825 23312825] {{Wayback|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23312825 |date=20200701105843 }}.</ref><ref>Morita Y, Sakagami Y, Okabe T, Ohe T, Inamori Y, Ishida N (September 2007). "The mechanism of the bactericidal activity of hinokitiol". Biocontrol Science. 12 (3): 101–10. [https://doi.org/10.4265%2Fbio.12.101 doi:10.4265/bio.12.101]. PMID [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17927050 17927050] {{Wayback|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17927050 |date=20210722211610 }}.</ref>

具体而言，已显示Hinokitiol对肺炎链球菌，变形链球菌和金黄色葡萄球菌（人类常见病原体）有效。<ref>Wang TH, Hsia SM, Wu CH, Ko SY, Chen MY, Shih YH, et al. (2016-09-28). "[https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5040402 Evaluation of the Antibacterial Potential of Liquid and Vapor Phase Phenolic Essential Oil Compounds against Oral Microorganisms]". PloS One. 11 (9): e0163147. [https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2016PLoSO..1163147W Bibcode:2016PLoSO..1163147W] {{Wayback|url=https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2016PLoSO..1163147W |date=20200611014012 }}. [https://doi.org/10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0163147 doi:10.1371/journal.pone.0163147]. PMC [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5040402 5040402]. PMID [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27681039 27681039] {{Wayback|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27681039 |date=20201006182033 }}.</ref><ref>Domon H, Hiyoshi T, Maekawa T, Yonezawa D, Tamura H, Kawabata S, et al. (June 2019). "Antibacterial activity of hinokitiol against both antibiotic-resistant and -susceptible pathogenic bacteria that predominate in the oral cavity and upper airways". Microbiology and Immunology. 63 (6): 213–222. [https://doi.org/10.1111%2F1348-0421.12688 doi:10.1111/1348-0421.12688]. PMID [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/31106894 31106894] {{Wayback|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/31106894 |date=20200709155812 }}.</ref>

另外，已显示Hinokitiol对[[沙眼衣原体|沙眼衣原体]]具有抑制作用，并且在临床上可用作局部用药。<ref>Yamano H, Yamazaki T, Sato K, Shiga S, Hagiwara T, Ouchi K, Kishimoto T (June 2005). "[https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC1140513 In vitro inhibitory effects of hinokitiol on proliferation of Chlamydia trachomatis]". Antimicrobial Agents and Chemotherapy. 49 (6): 2519–21. [https://doi.org/10.1128%2FAAC.49.6.2519-2521.2005 doi:10.1128/AAC.49.6.2519-2521.2005]. PMC [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC1140513 1140513]. PMID [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15917561 15917561] {{Wayback|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15917561 |date=20210810105904 }}.</ref><ref>Chedgy R (2010). Secondary metabolites of Western red cedar (Thujaplicata): their biotechnological applications and role in conferring natural durability. LAP Lambert Academic Publishing. ISBN [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-3-8383-4661-8 978-3-8383-4661-8].</ref>

===抗病毒活性===
最近的研究表明，Hinokitiol与锌化合物联合使用时，还对多种人类病毒（包括鼻病毒，柯萨奇病毒和芒果病毒）具有抗病毒作用。<ref name="KREN">Krenn BM, Gaudernak E, Holzer B, Lanke K, Van Kuppeveld FJ, Seipelt J (January 2009). "[https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2612303 Antiviral activity of the zinc ionophores pyrithione and hinokitiol against picornavirus infections] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2612303 |date=20210907103808 }}". Journal of Virology. 83 (1): 58–64. [https://doi.org/10.1128%2FJVI.01543-08 doi:10.1128/JVI.01543-08]. PMC [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2612303 2612303] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2612303 |date=20210907103808 }}. PMID [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18922875 18922875] {{Wayback|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18922875 |date=20211021223616 }}.</ref>

治愈病毒感染有可能获得大规模的经济利益，并且对诸如世界卫生组织这样的全球机构来说至关重要。通过削弱病毒多蛋白的加工，Hinokitiol抑制了病毒复制-但是，此功能取决于二价金属离子的可用性，因为Hinokitiol是其螯合剂。<ref>Krenn BM, Gaudernak E, Holzer B, Lanke K, Van Kuppeveld FJ, Seipelt J (January 2009). "[https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2612303 Antiviral activity of the zinc ionophores pyrithione and hinokitiol against picornavirus infections] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2612303 |date=20210907103808 }}". Journal of Virology. 83 (1): 58–64. [https://doi.org/10.1128%2FJVI.01543-08 doi:10.1128/JVI.01543-08]. PMC [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2612303 2612303] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2612303 |date=20210907103808 }}. PMID [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18922875 18922875] {{Wayback|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18922875 |date=20211021223616 }}.</ref> 锌与Hinokitiol的结合支持了这些功能，下面将进行讨论。

==其他活动==
除广谱抗菌活性外，Hinokitiol还具有抗炎和抗肿瘤活性，其特点是进行了许多体外细胞研究和体内动物研究。Hinokitiol可抑制关键的炎症标志物和途径，例如TNF-a和NF-kB，并且正在探索其治疗慢性炎症或自身免疫性疾病的潜力。发现Hinokitiol通过诱导自噬过程对几种重要的癌细胞系产生细胞毒性。<ref>Lee TB, Jun JH (2019-06-30). "Can Hinokitiol Kill Cancer Cells? Alternative Therapeutic Anticancer Agent via Autophagy and Apoptosis". Korean Journal of Clinical Laboratory Science. 51 (2): 221–234. [https://doi.org/10.15324%2Fkjcls.2019.51.2.221 doi:10.15324/kjcls.2019.51.2.221].</ref><ref>Jayakumar T, Liu CH, Wu GY, Lee TY, Manubolu M, Hsieh CY, et al. (March 2018). "[https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5979393 Hinokitiol Inhibits Migration of A549 Lung Cancer Cells via Suppression of MMPs and Induction of Antioxidant Enzymes and Apoptosis]". International Journal of Molecular Sciences. 19 (4): 939. [https://doi.org/10.3390%2Fijms19040939 doi:10.3390/ijms19040939]. PMC [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5979393 5979393]. PMID [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29565268 29565268] {{Wayback|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29565268 |date=20201006005137 }}.</ref>

===冠状病毒研究===
Hinokitiol作为锌离子载体的作用可能具有抗病毒作用。Hinokitiol使锌离子流入细胞，从而抑制RNA病毒的复制机制，并随后抑制病毒的复制。<ref name="KREN"/> 一些值得注意的RNA病毒包括人类流感病毒SARS。<ref name="TEV">teVelthuis AJ, van den Worm SH, Sims AC, Baric RS, Snijder EJ, van Hemert MJ (November 2010). "[https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2973827 Zn(2+) inhibits coronavirus and arterivirus RNA polymerase activity in vitro and zinc ionophores block the replication of these viruses in cell culture] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2973827 |date=20220102171111 }}". PLoS Pathogens. 6 (11): e1001176. [https://doi.org/10.1371%2Fjournal.ppat.1001176 doi:10.1371/journal.ppat.1001176]. PMC [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2973827 2973827] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2973827 |date=20220102171111 }}. PMID [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21079686 21079686] {{Wayback|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21079686 |date=20211221190057 }}.</ref> 锌离子能够显着抑制细胞内的病毒复制，并证明其作用取决于锌的流入。这项研究是用锌离子载体巯氧吡啶进行的，其功能与Hinokitiol非常相似。<ref name="TEV"/>

在细胞培养物中，扁柏酚可抑制人鼻病毒，柯萨奇病毒和芒果病毒的繁殖。Hinokitiol干扰病毒多蛋白的加工，从而抑制小核糖核酸病毒复制。Hinokitiol通过削弱病毒多蛋白加工来抑制小核糖核酸病毒的复制，并且hinokitiol的抗病毒活性取决于锌离子的可用性。<ref>Krenn BM, Gaudernak E, Holzer B, Lanke K, Van Kuppeveld FJ, Seipelt J (January 2009). "[https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2612303 Antiviral activity of the zinc ionophores pyrithione and hinokitiol against picornavirus infections] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2612303 |date=20210907103808 }}". Journal of Virology. 83 (1): 58–64. [https://doi.org/10.1128%2Fjvi.01543-08 doi:10.1128/jvi.01543-08]. PMC [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2612303 2612303] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2612303 |date=20210907103808 }}. PMID [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18922875 18922875] {{Wayback|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18922875 |date=20211021223616 }}</ref>

===铁离子载体===
已显示日香酚可以在啮齿动物中恢复血红蛋白的产生。Hinokitiol充当铁离子载体，将铁引导进入细胞，<ref>Grillo AS, SantaMaria AM, Kafina MD, Cioffi AG, Huston NC, Han M, et al. (May 2017). "[https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5470741 Restored iron transport by a small molecule promotes absorption and hemoglobinization in animals]". Science. 356 (6338): 608–616. [https://doi.org/10.1126%2Fscience.aah3862 doi:10.1126/science.aah3862]. PMC [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5470741 5470741]. PMID [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28495746 28495746].</ref><ref>Service RF (2017-05-11). "Iron Man molecule restores balance to cells". Science. AAAS. [https://doi.org/10.1126%2Fscience.aal1178 doi:10.1126/science.aal1178].</ref> 增加细胞内铁水平。人体中约70％的铁包含在红细胞中，尤其是血红蛋白。铁对几乎所有生物都是必不可少的，并且它是一些解剖功能的关键元素，例如氧气转运系统，脱氧核糖核酸（DNA）合成，电子转运和缺铁会导致血液疾病，例如贫血，对身体和心理表现均有害。<ref>Abbaspour N, Hurrell R, Kelishadi R (February 2014). "[https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3999603 Review on iron and its importance for human health] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3999603 |date=20211205220438 }}". Journal of Research in Medical Sciences. 19 (2): 164–74. PMC [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3999603 3999603] {{Wayback|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3999603 |date=20211205220438 }}. PMID [https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24778671 24778671] {{Wayback|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24778671 |date=20210928202726 }}</ref>

==锌协同作用==
Hinokitiol是锌离子载体，据信这种能力可抑制病毒复制。简而言之，作为锌离子载体，Hinokitiol有助于通过质膜或细胞内膜将分子运输到细胞中，从而增加特定分子（例如锌）的细胞内浓度。因此，通过利用锌的抗病毒特性，结合Hinokitiol，可以促进锌的吸收。<ref>"[https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/ionophores Ionophores - an overview - ScienceDirect Topics] {{Wayback|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/ionophores |date=20170706024128 }}". www.sciencedirect.com. Retrieved 2020-06-25.</ref>

